In [8]:
view_1 = pd.read_sql("""
SELECT 
    strftime('%Y-%m', Date) as month_year,
    Feature as feature,
    count(distinct Username) as total_users,
    sum(Sessions) as total_sessions,
    sum("Time spent") as total_time_spent
FROM usage u
WHERE 1=1 
GROUP BY 1,2
""", con=conn)
view_1

In [10]:
#filter df for yrs 2022 & 2023
view_1['month_year'] = pd.to_datetime(view_1['month_year'])
view_filtered = view_1[(view_1['month_year'].dt.year >= 2022) & (view_1['month_year'].dt.year <= 2023)]

#convert month_year back to string for plotting
view_filtered['month_year'] = view_filtered['month_year'].dt.strftime('%Y-%m')

#plot time series
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
sns.lineplot(data=view_filtered, x='month_year', y='total_users', hue='feature', linewidth=2.5, palette='tab10')

#customize plot
plt.title('Time Series of Total Users by Feature (2022-2023)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
plt.xlabel('Month-Year', fontweight='bold')
plt.ylabel('Total Number of Users', fontweight='bold')
plt.legend(title='Feature', fontsize='large', title_fontsize='13')

#rotate x-axis labels; show every other tick
plt.xticks(rotation=45)

#save plot w/ high resolution
plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig('time_series_total_users_2022_2023.png', dpi=300)

#show plot
plt.show()

#filter df for yrs 2022 & 2023
view_1['month_year'] = pd.to_datetime(view_1['month_year'])
view_filtered = view_1[(view_1['month_year'].dt.year >= 2022) & (view_1['month_year'].dt.year <= 2023)]

#convert month_year back to string for plotting
view_filtered['month_year'] = view_filtered['month_year'].dt.strftime('%Y-%m')

#plot time series
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
sns.lineplot(data=view_filtered, x='month_year', y='total_time_spent', hue='feature', linewidth=2.5, palette='tab10')

#customize plot
plt.title('Time Series of Total Time Spent by Feature (2022-2023)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
plt.xlabel('Month-Year', fontweight='bold')
plt.ylabel('Total Time Spent (sec.)', fontweight='bold')
plt.legend(title='Feature', fontsize='large', title_fontsize='13')

plt.xticks(rotation=45)
plt.gca().set_xticks(plt.gca().get_xticks()[::2])

plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig('time_series_total_time_spent_2022_2023.png', dpi=300)

plt.show()
